overview: Vic is tired of "dating down" and wants some security in her life. She meets Derrick, a handsome and generous man who whisks her and her best friend Bunny away to a luxury resort for the weekend. All seems to be perfect until she meets a handsome bartender with big dreams and an even bigger heart. Meanwhile all is not what it seems with Derrick. Torn between what her head wants and what her heart wants, Vic has to make a choice, but will she make the right one?
title: Last Call
